Macro to slide a block across surrounding text
Keywords: SLIDER TSE 2.0 MACRO BLOCK MOVE SLIDE PASTE OVER

Slide a column block over existing text. When it reaches its destination,
ENTER to paste it in place. The sliding block doesn't affect the layout of
text around it, making this macro well suited for modifying cloumnar data
such as menus and tables.

