Usage:


Load the macro. Mark a column block and run macro by hitting F12.

        CURSOR KEYS, TAB, SHIFT-TAB, PGUP, PGDN:  move the block.
        ENTER:  paste it over underlying text.
        ESC:  cancel the whole operation.

To assign macro to a key other than F12, edit lines 88 and 91 in SLIDER.S

